    {
      "id": "PopularPost371613",
      "post_content": "This is why I hate [lightning bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lightning bolt). Lightning bolt has set a stupidly high standard for red burn in the future, that (in my opinion), still hasn't been matched.  \n  \n3 dmg for 1 cmc is freakishly generous for removal, especially for removal with versatility. Compare this to all other 1 cmc removals from ALL other colors, and you find that it's very hard to find one that is consistently useful.   \n  \nCompare to [Essence Drain](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Essence Drain) [Sorin's Thirst](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sorin's Thirst), [Unsummon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Unsummon), [Prey Upon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prey Upon) etc etc etc.   \n  \nLightning Bolt is too much!",
      "posted_by": "Burningsickle",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost371613\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">This is why I hate <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"lightning bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lightning bolt\">lightning bolt</a>. Lightning bolt has set a stupidly high standard for red burn in the future, that (in my opinion), still hasn't been matched.<br/><br/>3 dmg for 1 cmc is freakishly generous for removal, especially for removal with versatility. Compare this to all other 1 cmc removals from ALL other colors, and you find that it's very hard to find one that is consistently useful. <br/><br/>Compare to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Essence Drain\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Essence Drain\">Essence Drain</a> <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sorin's Thirst\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sorin's Thirst\">Sorin's Thirst</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Unsummon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Unsummon\">Unsummon</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Prey Upon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prey Upon\">Prey Upon</a> etc etc etc. <br/><br/>Lightning Bolt is too much!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '371613'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"Po